{"tid":1068264,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"阿妹帶咗個男朋友返嚟見家長","createTime":"2019-03-19T06:05:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-20T17:35:26.000Z","uid":48286,"like":60,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"2d5ef67e963daa172c9c45b1c58d229decf1207e","tid":1068264,"uid":48286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T06:05:21.000Z","msg":"件事係上星期日，老母突然叫我返去食飯，原來阿妹帶咗個男朋友返嚟見家長，雖然個男ge毒毒地但都叫有齊眼耳口鼻，家庭背境合格，老母開頭都好滿意，有講有笑咁，個晚餐飯冇煮雞所以冇雞脾食<br />\n<br />\n食到中段問到個男ge做邊行個陣，佢話銀行，老母面帶笑容，再問:<br />\n母 : 邊個銀行?<br />\n毒 : 大眾銀行<br />\n母 : 面色一沉，大眾？<br />\n阿妹即時加把口，都係大銀行嚟！<br />\n母 : 咁你做咩位?<br />\n毒 : 客戶經理 (好似係，佢越講越細聲)<br />\n母 : 係分行返工?<br />\n毒 : 唔係，主要係聯絡客戶<br />\n母 : 咁即係亂打電話個D<strong>仆街</strong>?<br />\n毒 : er..........<br />\n妹 : 媽.....<br />\n<br />\n跟住全餐飯就好靜，我唯有開電視睇東張西望<br />\ncold call 狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d72d5f62a15fb7016fb15c3f8723c44c8b926ff0","tid":1068264,"uid":95637,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T06:08:36.000Z","msg":"你吖媽啱喎"},{"pid":"8fdc160d5ec2a78b959f772aa8cff80652bd8a98","tid":1068264,"uid":48286,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"quote":{"pid":"d72d5f62a15fb7016fb15c3f8723c44c8b926ff0","tid":1068264,"uid":95637,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T06:08:36.000Z","msg":"你吖媽啱喎"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T06:12:35.000Z","msg":"佢最憎cold call 狗<br />\n歸類為詐騙電話"},{"pid":"a9c5aeb84aaf86b10a762e02973f6873a4b533ce","tid":1068264,"uid":196924,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T06:13:08.000Z","msg":"伯友都係講事實"},{"pid":"08163535470cf1e15e363ff49a40edc98b2e850d","tid":1068264,"uid":57862,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T05:27:04.000Z","msg":"唉<br />\n都叫有女呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/tongue.gif\" 